{"tid":684102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生secret: 葵青區某學校 要求學生簽回條同意錄影上堂情況並寄俾教育局","createTime":"2018-05-30T08:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T12:13:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"730fbd368bc59da867235e2f79ebaf70d9b3669f","tid":684102,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"#HKStudentSecret1209<br />\n<br />\n[葵青區][LC]<br />\n［扮民主］我個一間學校係上年上堂錄影我哋嘅課堂比教育局睇， 咁今年就叫我地簽回條， 佢有得俾你揀同意同埋唔同意， 咁小妹我就揀咗唔同意 <br />\n<br />\n但係我估唔到佢一個月之後過嚟我哋班到宣布要我地改返同意 仲要打俾我哋家長？<br />\n<br />\n其實如果係一開始就要我哋同意嘅話我就會接受，但係佢有得俾你揀但係又唔俾你揀同意好矛盾，而且佢哋宣布嘅時候態度都唔係好好， 好似講到錄影我哋嘅課堂係理所當然，仲要話如果唔同意就要用特別處理手法 ，如果你咁樣我真係想講，你開始直接係通告上面寫明白就算數啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkstudent.secrets/posts/2048262205440437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkstudent.secrets%2Fposts%2F2048262205440437&d=PTTdPivMZrlUXxKst%2FMdAUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0cb5ad53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkstudent.secrets/posts/2048262205440437</a>"},{"pid":"8d13c431bd2151700fcc5597095d93ed8da3af0a","tid":684102,"uid":66686,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"名都唔敢開就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ebb66badc3f2ea1a26fe02625a9903cbc8d793","tid":684102,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d13c431bd2151700fcc5597095d93ed8da3af0a","tid":684102,"uid":66686,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"名都唔敢開就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"咪就係"},{"pid":"3529b2cbbce00e347314c22f6adf73832fefddc0","tid":684102,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"唔響朵點幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cadd7f4233b919356ec3022d1